@ENDNODE

@NODE Requirements "Requirements"
@TOC Main
MagicSelector should run on any Amiga system with at least 512K RAM and:

@{b}MagicSelector requires:@{ub}

 KickStart v3.0 or greater (Sorry 2.x people!)
 asl.library
 datatype.library
 8SVX datatype
 MUImaster.library V2.2+
 MUI-Classes
 Sys:Prefs/WBPattern
 sys:Prefs/Sound

I have not included MUI since this would have made the archive a lot bigger. If the MUI-package is not yet in your possession, you should be able to find it at several Public Domain sites around the world, your local BBS or on Public Domain Disks.

The Graphical User Interface (GUI) was created using the great MUImaster.library V2.2 @{" MUI " LINK MUI}, Copyrighted 1992/94 Stefan Stuntz.


@ENDNODE

