     Own listviews for Workbench, Windows and Screen.
     Removed Checkmark buttons, No function anymore.
     Safer error handling in both program.
     Removed all 4 enforcer hit in the prefs program.

   @{b}Version 1.20@{ub}         (30.8.94)
     Added locale support
     Listviews are not longer in alphabetic order.
     Added Movement button on all listviews.
     Added preview doubleclick on entry for background and sound.
     Software changed to ShareWare.

